{"tid":1867687,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"政府眼中，公務員係condom","createTime":"2020-02-07T09:33:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T05:43:35.000Z","uid":317316,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6f8e673e016b47d3b0e5556b307cee21239b4ad9","tid":1867687,"uid":317316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T09:33:45.000Z","msg":"非緊急公務員祝好運<br />\n<br />\n政府強制要求公務員去「隔離營」做「義工」！<br />\n<br />\n收到公務員報料，各部門主管今日被要求提交名單，名單上的人需不日到隔離營做「義務工作」，包括看守被隔離人士。<br />\n<br />\n該公務員透露，自己並非technical grade (專業職系) 員工，完全沒有醫療背景，只屬普通職系，但他已被上司交名，知道其他部門亦有同樣情況，而事前是沒有收到任何知會及通知，感到非常憤怒。<br />\n<br />\n同時，政府亦已羅列至少5項義務工作給被交名的公務員，當中最令人詫異的B、C兩點，須進行高風險工作。<br />\n<br />\n(B) 隨機家訪，到被隔離人士的住處，檢查是否在家。<br />\n<br />\n(C) 守隔離營，看守並不准被隔離人士離開。<br />\n<br />\n「連看守隔離營都要我哋普通同事負責，究竟紀律部隊做乜嘢？！」該公務員質疑是警員不願做的dirty work，政府將其攤分給其他部門，坦言這舉動絕不合理，並非沒有醫療背景的普通公務員可以負責。<br />\n<br />\n政府宣布午夜起，從內地入境人士將被強制隔離檢疫14日。據了解，西貢麥理浩夫人度假村、鯉魚門公園度假村、八鄉少年警訊中心，三個地方亦會用作檢疫中心，當局正在興建組合屋，主要被安排被強制檢疫人士暫住。<br />\n<br />\n暫時未知「被交名」的公務員，何時需要到以上的隔離營提供「義務工作」。<br />\n<br />\n新公務員工會 Union for New Civil Servants"},{"pid":"da99660732553d0aba994c8fef0f0de1e940a657","tid":1867687,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T09:42:44.000Z","msg":"等班公務員個個拎口罩派親戚咁過癮丫拿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9c49d5589f1047d3cd464c30c6614fa7d07f7a5","tid":1867687,"uid":192630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T09:45:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J50CmvY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ50CmvY.jpg&h=6a2c5316&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/hkonstrike/1040\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike%2F1040&d=uFnVTFPFhHj2sSFH0VdWwSBot4r0pQQ4M2eut5PfJzM%3D&h=dc8499a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/hkonstrike/1040</a><br />\n立即加入 罷工救港"},{"pid":"19a9bbe2cd977e17159ef9021fc5bd5fd05146f8","tid":1867687,"uid":14337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T09:46:24.000Z","msg":"做老屎忽就好<br />\n出世同生活都美好<br />\n返工又A字膊 得閒又偷口罩發上國難財<br />\n宜家有事又推D後生去死"},{"pid":"2c45f0e60060ccdabd124edf6dc8234b4a883280","tid":1867687,"uid":293543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T09:47:54.000Z","msg":"林奠講到明得3萬個黑警"},{"pid":"96da76c875050c47d4ffbbdf167d403a21bf2fa9","tid":1867687,"uid":317316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c45f0e60060ccdabd124edf6dc8234b4a883280","tid":1867687,"uid":293543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T09:47:54.000Z","msg":"林奠講到明得3萬個黑警"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T09:48:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aad104256d692df232e5725ea511a1b4313b6b5","tid":1867687,"uid":123738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:00:21.000Z","msg":"依家領導叫佢地去死，即刻好開心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0e19fc7c13edb7766f6f9befc91241c512ba60f","tid":1867687,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3aad104256d692df232e5725ea511a1b4313b6b5","tid":1867687,"uid":123738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:00:21.000Z","msg":"依家領導叫佢地去死，即刻好開心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T05:43:35.000Z","msg":"藍屍公務員會好enjoy"}]}